under this warranty?","answer":"<p>If your product develops an issue within the 3-year coverage period under normal use, Dr. Water will repair or replace it free of charge and send a replacement promptly so you can continue using it without interruption.<br\/><\/p>"}},"faq_c6Ae3a":{"type":"faq","settings":{"question":"Can existing customers add the 3-Year Extended Warranty later?","answer":"<p>Yes, existing product owners can still add the extended warranty. Contact the Dr. Water support team with your order details to confirm eligibility and receive a purchase link. Coverage starts as soon as you buy it.<\/p>"}},"faq_nYaFxx":{"type":"faq","settings":{"question":"How can I purchase and activate the extended warranty?","answer":"<p>You can add the warranty to your cart along with your Dr. Water product, or purchase it separately if you already own the product.<br\/><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["faq_46ddbg","faq_HU94GN","faq_kexdpd","faq_dRDjab","faq_c6Ae3a","faq_nYaFxx"],"name":"FAQ Dropdown Section","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Got Questions? We've Got Answers<\/strong>","footer_title":"Didn't find the answer you're looking for?","footer_text":"We're here to help—reach out to our friendly team anytime for support and guidance.","footer_button_text":"Ask a Question","footer_button_link":""}}},"order":["main","1771680482a5a62d55","rich_text_fgzHtR","custom_liquid_PqnWjE","custom_liquid_MzJw6T","rich_text_jFkdb9","rich_text_WMpLTm","faq_fAaBjP"]}